  "lastUpdatedOn": "2013-02-11",
  "religion": "Gerard Piqué is most likely Catholic, and probably not terribly devout.",
  "politicalViews": "He is non-political.",
  "author": "Caitlin Frye",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Gerard Piqué was born and raised in Barcelona, Spain."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "It sure would make sense if Piqué was Catholic, and I'm not the only one who's guessing that to be true.",
      "sourceTitle": "Celebrity Religion – Roman Catholic (Celebrities): G.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.whosdatedwho.com/sections/celebrities/religion/roman-catholic_g"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "After all, he is a Spaniard.",
      "parentId": 2,
      "sourceTitle": "Religion in Spain.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Religion_in_Spain"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Plus his baby momma, Shakira, is Catholic. But, like Shakira, Piqué doesn't appear to be particularly devout. He doesn't talk about God or praying on his Twitter feed and he doesn't wear a cross around.",
      "parentId": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "But, he did visit the Wailing Wall in Jerusalem, and appeared to pray while resting his yarmulke-covered head against the holy spot.",
      "sourceTitle": "Gerard Pique & Shakira Visit Jerusalem's Western Wall (Photos).",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/miscellaneous/75490/gerard-pique-shakira-visit-jerusalems-western-wall-photos.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I guess that makes him sound more like a Jew than a Catholic, doesn't it? But maybe he was just following in the footsteps of the Pope.",
      "parentId": 3,
      "sourceTitle": "Raw Video: Pope Visits Western Wall in Jerusalem.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gg3QR3z5_Uw"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Plus a lot of non-Jews wear yarmulkes at the Western Wall,",
      "parentId": 3,
      "sourceTitle": "Romney's Western Wall note removed.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.timesofisrael.com/romneys-western-wall-note-removed/"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "including the Pope! Except his isn't a yarmulke, it's a zucchetto, which is a Catholic thing. So maybe that's what Piqué was wearing on his visit, except that usually only. . . you know what. I need to stop. He's not Jewish, okay?",
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 4
    },
    {
      "parentId": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Let's conclude with all signs pointing to not terribly devout, but at least a little religious, Catholic."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Shaqué, or is Piquira?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "If Piqué isn't terribly religious, he's not terribly political either, despite the fact that"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 6,
      "type": "emphasis",
      "text": "Forbes"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "magazine named him and Shakira one of the 15 most powerful couples in 2012.",
      "parentId": 6,
      "sourceTitle": "Shakira and Gerard Pique – The World's 15 Most Powerful Couples in 2012.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.forbes.com/pictures/lmj45kefh/shakira-and-gerard-pique/"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "They did use their position of power, however, to garner some donations for UNICEF, the United Nations' fund for children. A few weeks after their baby boy was born, they posted a picture on their website, but would only let fans see it if they made a small donation to the organization.",
      "parentId": 6,
      "sourceTitle": "Shakira and Gerard Piqué Introduce Son Milan.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://celebritybabies.people.com/2013/02/04/shakira-gerard-pique-son-milan-first-photo/"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 7
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Maybe we'll see more from Piqué's side of the Shaqué power couple as he settles into fatherhood. Or maybe we won't. But you'll keep us updated in the comments, right?"
    }
  ],
